org.princehouse.mica.base.model
Class RuntimeAgent<P extends Protocol>

java.lang.Object
  org.princehouse.mica.base.model.RuntimeAgent<P>
Type Parameters:
P - 
public abstract class RuntimeAgent<P extends Protocol>
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the "compiled" protocol to the MiCA Runtime. A Compiler instance takes a Protocol implementation class and emits a RuntimeAgent for that class. RuntimeAgent knows how to execute the distributed update function. Any analysis results from the original Protocol class are stored in the RuntimeAgent.

Author:
lonnie
